; “will; be going to; near” (Pronunciation 1)
: {{der|zh|aav}}: compare {{cog|km|ចង់||to want, to wish; to approach, to draw near; about to (do something), on the point of}} < {{cog|okz|caṅa||to wish, to want}}. Cognate with {{och-l|且|about to; on the point of; moreover; also}} ({{zh-ref|Wu, 2015}}).

